rse.go`\n  - `FormatStreamJSON()` - converts raw Claude Code stream-json output to human-readable text\n  - Parses event types: `content_block_start`, `content_block_delta`, `content_block_stop`, `message_stop`, `result`\n  - Extracts text content and tool names from stream\n  - `IsStreamJSON()` - detects if content is Claude Code stream-json format\n  - Returns original if parsing fails (graceful fallback)\n\n### 3. **Web UI Display**\n\n#### Log Streaming for Active Runs:\n- **Broadcaster** (`/workspace/internal/logstream/broadcaster.go`):\n  - `Broadcaster` struct manages real-time log distribution\n  - `Subscribe()` - clients subscribe to a run's log stream\n  - `Publish()` - broadcasts LogLine to all subscribers with non-blocking delivery\n  - `Finish()` - closes all subscriber channels when run completes\n  - `LogLine` struct: Timestamp, Type, Content\n\n#### Handler Functions (`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`):\n\n1. **handleAPIStream** (lines 721-780):\n   - Server-Sent Events (SSE) endpoint at `/api/runs/{id}/stream`\n   - For active runs: subscribes to logBroadcast and streams live updates\n   - For completed runs: reads archived full.log file\n   - Sends \"done\" event with final run state\n\n2. **streamFullLog** (lines 786-802):\n   - Reads `.cloche/{runID}/output/full.log` line by line\n   - Parses \"[timestamp] [type] content\" format via regex\n   - Converts to LogLine JSON and sends as SSE events\n\n3. **parseFullLogLine** (lines 805-819):\n   - Regex: `^\\[([^\\]]+)\\] \\[([^\\]]+)\\] (.*)$`\n   - Extracts timestamp, type, content from full.log lines\n\n4. **handleAPIStepOutput** (lines 564-639):\n   - JSON endpoint at `/api/runs/{id}/steps/{step}/output`\n   - Retrieves step-specific logs with optional filtering by type\n   - Priority: log index → file path conventions → live docker logs\n   - Calls `logparse.FormatStreamJSON()` unless format=raw\n   - Log file lookup order:\n     - `{outputDir}/llm-{step}.log` (if type==\"llm\")\n     - `{outputDir}/{step}.log` (per-step output)\n     - `{outputDir}/container.log` (fallback)\n     - Live Docker logs from container if still running\n\n#### Templates (`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/`):\n\n1. **run_detail.html** (lines 1-238):\n   - Log viewer section: `<div id=\"log-viewer\">` with pre-formatted content\n   - Step execution table with clickable rows\n   - Real-time log status badge showing \"Live\" or \"Complete\"\n   - JavaScript:\n     - Connects to SSE stream at `/api/runs/{runID}/stream`\n     - `appendLogLine()` - adds log entries to DOM with type-based CSS classes\n     - Auto-scroll enabled while at bottom; disabled when scrolled up\n     - Poll updates for steps every 2 seconds during active runs\n     - Click handlers for expandable step output rows\n     - Fetches step output from `/api/runs/{runID}/steps/{step}/output`\n\n2. **runs.html** (lines 1-106):\n   - Lists all runs with state, workflow, started/completed times\n   - Truncated error messages (80 chars)\n   - Project filter dropdown\n   - Polls `/api/runs` every 3 seconds for updates\n\n3. **layout.html** and **projects.html**:\n   - Mini run history (recent dots with color-coded states)\n   - Project health indicators\n\n### 4. **CLI Log Display**\n\n#### Command: `cloche logs` (`/workspace/cmd/cloche/main.go`, lines 223-304):\n\n- Subcommand: `logs <run-id> [--step <name>] [--type <full|script|llm>] [--follow]`\n- **Without --follow**: \n  - Calls gRPC `StreamLogs()` RPC\n  - Streams LogEntry messages\n  - Handles types: \"step_started\", \"step_completed\", \"run_completed\", \"full_log\", \"*_log\"\n- **With --follow** (`cmdLogsFollow`, lines 306-366):\n  - Connects to HTTP SSE endpoint at `/api/runs/{runID}/stream`\n  - Parses JSON log entries\n  - Color codes by type: blue=status, green=llm, default=script\n  - Terminates on \"event: done\"\n\n#### gRPC Log Streaming (`/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`, lines 458-634):\n\n1. **StreamLogs** (lines 458-555):\n   - Primary entry point for CLI log requests\n   - If no step/type filter:\n     - Tries to read `full.log` first (preferred unified log)\n     - Falls back to capture-based streaming\n     - Sends step_started, step_completed, run_completed entries\n   - Supports filtering by step and/or type\n\n2. **streamFilteredLogs** (lines 559-634):\n   - Filters logs by step name and/or type\n   - Uses LogStore index for fast lookup when available\n   - Falls back to file path conventions\n   - Reads from indexed file paths and sends content\n\n### 5. **Key Data Structures**\n\n- **StepExecution** (`/workspace/internal/domain/run.go`):\n  - StepName, Result, StartedAt, CompletedAt, Logs, GitRef\n\n- **LogLine** (`/workspace/internal/logstream/logstream.go`):\n  - JSON: Timestamp, Type, Content\n\n- **LogFileEntry** (`/workspace/internal/ports/store.go`):\n  - Database index of log files with paths and metadata\n\n- **LogEntry** (gRPC proto):\n  - Type, StepName, Result, Message, Timestamp\n\n### 6. **File Locations**\n\nAll log output is stored in: `{projectDir}/.cloche/{runID}/output/`\n- `full.log` - unified master log with all entries\n- `{stepName}.log` - per-step script output\n- `llm-{stepName}.log` - Claude Code agent output\n- `container.log` - internal Docker container logs (not indexed)\n\n### 7. **Flow Summary**\n\n**Writing**: Container execution → captured to files → logstream.Writer appends to full.log → indexLogFiles() indexes in SQLite\n\n**Display (Web UI)**:\n- Active: SSE broadcasts from logstream.Broadcaster → run_detail.html appends DOM elements\n- Completed: full.log read line-by-line → SSE stream → run_detail.html displays\n\n**Display (CLI)**:\n- gRPC StreamLogs RPC → reads from indexed log files → LogEntry messages → pretty printed\n\n**Absolute paths to key files:**\n- `/workspace/internal/logstream/logstream.go` - log file writing\n- `/workspace/internal/logstream/broadcaster.go` - live streaming\n- `/workspace/internal/logparse/parse.go` - Claude Code stream parsing\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go` - web API endpoints\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/run_detail.html` - log viewer UI\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go` - gRPC streaming and indexing\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/sqlite/store.go` - log database persistence\n- `/workspace/internal/ports/store.go` - LogStore interface\n- `/workspace/cmd/cloche/main.go` - CLI log commands\n- `/workspace/api/proto/cloche/v1/cloche.proto` - gRPC service definition"}],"totalDurationMs":60118,"totalTokens":68133,"totalToolUseCount":37,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1343,"cache_read_input_tokens":64223,"output_tokens":2567,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1343},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
